Feedback:

`_` (sequence.wipple:24:14-24:15) (conflicting-types)

  `_` (sequence.wipple:24:14-24:15) is a `String` (sequence.wipple:23:17-23:23) or a `Number` (sequence.wipple:24:19-24:25), but it can only be one of these.
  
  `_` (sequence.wipple:24:14-24:15) must be the same type as `_ :: Number` (sequence.wipple:24:14-24:25), `String` (sequence.wipple:23:17-23:23), `Number` (sequence.wipple:24:19-24:25), and 17 others; double-check these.
  
  -  `_` requires `As-Sequence` `_` `_`.
  
  -  `item` (sequence.wipple:20:12-20:16) must have the same type everywhere in this use of `filter` (sequence.wipple:25:2-25:8).
  
  -  `value` (sequence.wipple:18:28-18:33) must have the same type everywhere in this use of `_`.
